<!--<h4>First Section.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīmatu yādavanārāyaṇaṁ pratāpabhujabaḷacakravartti śrīsiṁ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ghaḷadēvavarusada 18 vijeyasaṁvatsarada phālguṇa sudha paṁcami sō
<lb n="3" break="no"/>mavāradalu nūṟuṁbāḍada Aṁtaravaḷḷiya staḷada kuṟubara kāṭigau
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ḍa kaṁcigauṁḍiya maga baṁmagauḍa nāḍōḍi vulihaḷiyalidali pāṁ
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Section.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḍyadēvanavaru <unclear>vu</unclear>lihaḷiyaniṟidalli tuṟuvaṁ maraḷci taḷuti
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṟidu meṟedu baṁmagauṇḍa suralōkapāptanāda <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="7"/>maṁgaḷa mahāśrī śrī © ©
</p>

